Statements: For making decisions
-if Statement
 Syntax:
        if(condition)
        {
           //This will execute only if condition is true
        }

 -if else statement
         if(condition)
         {
            //This will execute only if condition is true
         }
         else
         {
            //This will execute only if condition is false
         }

 In multiple if-else statement, if the last statement fails, else will also be executed

 - if else if statement
   if(condition)
   {
           //This will execute only if condition is true
   }
   else if(condition2)
   {
        //This will execute only if condition is true
   }
   else if(condition3)
      {
           //This will execute only if condition is true
      }
      else if(conditionN)
            {
                 //This will execute only if condition is true
            }
      else
      {
            //This will execute only if condition is false
      }